{"tid":2121274,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工程師涉機場阻差辦公 警員稱被告「感覺上」有意護送疑犯離開","createTime":"2020-07-23T08:09:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T15:51:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"472ec3e9ea910abe7856fa23e9ac7823a3d1afd8","tid":2121274,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/J6MZNGONWUTH3LUYHIGJYR7I5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FJ6MZNGONWUTH3LUYHIGJYR7I5A%2F&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=ece402ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200723%2FJ6MZNGONWUTH3LUYHIGJYR7I5A%2F&h=f5b7a266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200723/J6MZNGONWUTH3LUYHIGJYR7I5A/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年8月網民發起機場「和你飛」集會，其間爆發警民衝突，多人被捕。年輕工程師被指當日「搶犯」，阻撓警員制服另一名示威者，被控阻差辦公罪。案件今在沙田裁判法院開審。案中警員供稱，案發時該名男示威者躲到被告身後，被告見狀隨即伸手阻撓警員，「感覺上」有意護送男子離開。惟警員坦言視線集中在該男示威者身上，沒有留意被告何時介入兩人之間，亦無留意他原本身處的位置，僅稱他「應該喺左邊攝入嚟」。"},{"pid":"8e4b0582e8faa5df8cbeac4ec142f8f573304c7e","tid":2121274,"uid":174013,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:10:34.000Z","msg":"可靠證人<br />\n可靠感覺<br />\n罪成坐一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5866564bcb00cd0a559e7a096923e6f09fa0aabd","tid":2121274,"uid":151313,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:12:14.000Z","msg":"以感覺入罪<br />\n我感覺到你將來會犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d42d98842661c4a20bf42bf06fe99c5dba89818","tid":2121274,"uid":356914,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"又無理拉人 同新疆一樣 支共太可怕"},{"pid":"05c3a2feab6c2373bea3210365d25e7a2b9e22ed","tid":2121274,"uid":323319,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"憑感覺判案<img src=\"/asset